    "description": "<strong>舒服点，戴上耳机，潜入蝴蝶的梦境</strong><br>蝴蝶梦是一种沉思和放松的体验。没有敌人，没有目标，也没有匆忙。飞来飞去，拍几张照片，享受一个美丽的风格化世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松的体验等着你</h2>成为生活和程式化世界中的蝴蝶。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/af7ac4068b0e85e6960f0c627e6027fe.poster.avif?t=1717697480\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/af7ac4068b0e85e6960f0c627e6027fe.webm?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/af7ac4068b0e85e6960f0c627e6027fe.mp4?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵感来自中国传统山水画</h2>你所看到的每一个地方都可能是一幅美丽而平静的画面.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/035de07d3d7d582243fc0aec53124060.poster.avif?t=1717697480\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/035de07d3d7d582243fc0aec53124060.webm?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/035de07d3d7d582243fc0aec53124060.mp4?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索一个活生生的世界</h2>飞过天空，进入树林，飞越水面，降落在树木和岩石上。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/73fcd282f8ec97d44280cc524edcaf0b.poster.avif?t=1717697480\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/73fcd282f8ec97d44280cc524edcaf0b.webm?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/73fcd282f8ec97d44280cc524edcaf0b.mp4?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拍一张大自然的照片</h2>拍摄生活世界中的风景和野生动物。如果游戏对您来说太无聊，请尝试拍摄所有隐藏的东西！有100多个。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/42f402a23fcdc35b33176526eb04a487.poster.avif?t=1717697480\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/42f402a23fcdc35b33176526eb04a487.webm?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/42f402a23fcdc35b33176526eb04a487.mp4?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一点哲学</h2>寻找庄子大师，冥想现实的本质。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/e114c4f7906648fa9539e625edda46fb.poster.avif?t=1717697480\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/e114c4f7906648fa9539e625edda46fb.webm?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880640/extras/e114c4f7906648fa9539e625edda46fb.mp4?t=1717697480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>禅宗公案系列</strong><br>《蝶梦》取材于道家大哲学家庄子大师的禅宗公案。公案是一个故事、对话、问题或陈述，在禅修中用来引发“大怀疑”并练习或测试学生在禅宗方面的进步。<br><br><strong>关于我们</strong><br><br>The Philosophical School of Games 是一家来自巴西的小型工作室。我们的目标是创造美丽、放松和身临其境的小体验，触动玩家的心灵和灵魂。从宗教到哲学等等，请关注我们并查看我们的游戏。",
